\&  use Bio::Matrix::Scoring;
.Ve
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
.IX Header "DESCRIPTION"
An object which can handle \s-1AA\s0 or \s-1NT\s0 scoring matrix information.  Some
transformation properties are available too.
